title: 70000+ Quotes with Emoji Icons
summary: Over 70000 quotes in about 120 categories, shown with beautiful emoji icons.
description: More than 70000 quotes in the following categories (on your Android phones, tablets, or watches!): in each category are presented with an appropriate and beautifully designed large-sized emoji icon. You can also add any selected quote to your favorites or email it to anyone you like.Android Wear is also supported so you can enjoy all the quotes on your watch without even pulling out your smart phone or tablet.
